OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779663786
OL,3,COver 50,000 people ordered to evacuate
OL,4,Cas California chemical tank could
OL,5,Cexplode
OL,7,FMore than 50,000 people in Southern
OL,8,FCalifornia have been ordered to
OL,9,Fevacuate their homes because of a
OL,10,Fdamaged chemical tank that is at risk
OL,11,Fof exploding.
OL,13,FOfficials in the region are racing to
OL,14,Fcool down a huge tank filled with a
OL,15,Ftoxic chemical in GKN Aerospace in
OL,16,FGarden Grove as residents have been
OL,17,Fwarned a possible blast could cause
OL,18,Fcatastrophic damage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779663786
OL,3,COver 50,000 people ordered to evacuate
OL,4,Cas California chemical tank could
OL,5,Cexplode
OL,7,FThe chemical inside the tank, methyl
OL,8,Fmethacrylate, or MMA, can cause
OL,9,Frespiratory issues and irritation to
OL,10,Fthe skin and eyes, according to the
OL,11,FEnvironmental Protection Agency.
OL,13,FNo injuries have been reported and air
OL,14,Fmonitoring tests have so far found
OL,15,Fthat air pollution around the
OL,16,Fevacuation zone is so far within
OL,17,Fnormal limits.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
