OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779663786
OL,3,COver 50,000 people ordered to evacuate
OL,4,Cas California chemical tank could
OL,5,Cexplode
OL,7,FLocal authorities first intervened on
OL,8,FThursday when one of the tanks started
OL,9,Fto overheat but parts of the self-
OL,10,Fcooling system weren't working and the
OL,11,Ftemperature continued to increase.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
