SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779663786
OL,3,COver 50,000 people ordered to evacuate
OL,4,Cas California chemical tank could
OL,5,Cexplode
OL,7,FMethyl methacrylate's "happy place" is
OL,8,F50 degrees, Orange County Fire
OL,9,FAuthority Division Chief and Unified
OL,10,FIncident Commander Craig Covey said on
OL,11,FFriday, but the tank is thought to
OL,12,Fhave reached temperatures of 90
OL,13,Fdegrees.
OL,26,@oD@WOUoD@cO]
