PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779663786
OL,3,COver 50,000 people ordered to evacuate
OL,4,Cas California chemical tank could
OL,5,Cexplode
OL,7,F"Right now, this is an emergency
OL,8,Fresponse. This isn't yet an
OL,9,Fenvironmental response, and the scale
OL,10,Fof that environmental response will be
OL,11,Fdetermined based off of what happens
OL,12,Fwhen that tank fails," Environmental
OL,13,FProtection Agency Administrator Lee
OL,14,FZeldin said on Sunday.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
