FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779663786
OL,3,COver 50,000 people ordered to evacuate
OL,4,Cas California chemical tank could
OL,5,Cexplode
OL,7,FThe fire authority released a blast
OL,8,Fzone map on Saturday outlining areas
OL,9,Fthat could be impacted if the tank
OL,10,Fexplodes. The map shows three rings
OL,11,Faround the facility representing zones
OL,12,Fof severe, moderate and light
OL,13,Fstructural damage.
OL,15,F"Letting this thing just fail and blow
OL,16,Fup is unacceptable to us. Our goal is
OL,17,Fto find something and not allow that
OL,18,Fhappen, not to let it damage our
OL,19,Fcommunity, not let it damage our
OL,20,Fenvironment," Covey said.
OL,26,@wD@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
