PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779663786
OL,3,COver 50,000 people ordered to evacuate
OL,4,Cas California chemical tank could
OL,5,Cexplode
OL,7,FGKN apologised to evacuated residents
OL,8,Fand businesses in a statement on
OL,9,FSaturday and said it is working with
OL,10,Femergency services and hazardous
OL,11,Fmaterials teams "to ensure the safety
OL,12,Fof the local community, our employees
OL,13,Fand everyone else involved."
